Welcome to SilverStack Jenkins Lab! 🚀

Jenkins is running internally at http://localhost:__JENKINS_PORT__
Nginx reverse proxy is listening on port 80 (internal)

Tools:

- cloudflared         Cloudflare Tunnel for public access
- java 21             Modern LTS Java runtime
- arkade  jq  yq  fx  task  just  fzf  btop  cfssl  ripgrep

To expose Jenkins publicly via Cloudflare Tunnel:

  1. one.dash.cloudflare.com → Networks → Connectors
  2. Create tunnel → name it (e.g. jenkins-lab) → choose Cloudflared
  3. Copy & run the install command shown:
       sudo cloudflared service install <token>
  4. Route Traffic → Add public hostname:
       Subdomain: jenkins   Domain: yourdomain.com
       Service:   HTTP      URL:    localhost:80
  5. Jenkins is now live at https://jenkins.yourdomain.com

Quick commands:
  jenkins-status  jenkins-logs  jenkins-restart  jenkins-start  jenkins-stop
  nginx-status    nginx-logs    nginx-reload
